{"tid":1216781,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先救左隻貓仔 俾返佢老母 佢老母轉個頭又掉左佢 點算好","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T06:29:10.000Z","uid":89584,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4b50acaa562390db0600872b74ef3140af8ec41d","tid":1216781,"uid":89584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"今日一路聽到出面有貓仔叫 發現佢係喺個比鐵絲網圍住嘅私人地到(村屋撚)<br />\n我搵條梯跳入去之後執左佢出黎 有隻唔知係咪佢老母嘅貓跑左過黎<br />\n我放低隻貓仔 隻老母就擔走左佢<br />\n然後過幾個鐘之後隻貓仔又係幅私人地到係咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該點算好<br />\n利伸1:唔打算養<br />\n利伸2:跳入去果陣屎忽落地 依家已經冇力跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3227852fae072c71bb929c2b211b18ba381a9ecd","tid":1216781,"uid":30325,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:01:11.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37157222603a89f4c69f9e5ac4cc15e58026644e","tid":1216781,"uid":258187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"執起佢 開 post送人。"},{"pid":"4b002307ae4c4658ffcaa16097fbe9242373ac16","tid":1216781,"uid":89584,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37157222603a89f4c69f9e5ac4cc15e58026644e","tid":1216781,"uid":258187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"執起佢 開 post送人。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"屎忽傷左 冇能力再入多次去果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350371422ccdd7fe8ed5ac7d917e89d63ab8c012","tid":1216781,"uid":89584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n佢老母係本來係野貓 有戶人整左個膠箱 比佢係門口訓<br />\n隻貓仔未開眼 不過識爬"},{"pid":"9452e81c5d692451a9d82d60e4fd0837b37e3899","tid":1216781,"uid":7476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"貓媽 已經認唔到佢 冇左d味"},{"pid":"d671e0ff99264b65ebe5fc40765e9c452e8a3e